Package org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.data

Interface DataInstance

All Superinterfaces:
BaseElement, BonitaObject, NamedElement, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
ArchivedDataInstance
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArchivedDataInstanceImpl, BlobDataInstanceImpl, BooleanDataInstanceImpl, DataInstanceImpl, DateDataInstanceImpl, DoubleDataInstanceImpl, FloatDataInstanceImpl, IntegerDataInstanceImpl, LongDataInstanceImpl, LongTextDataInstanceImpl, ShortTextDataInstanceImpl
public interface DataInstance extends NamedElement, BaseElement
This object represents this instance of DataDefinition generated when the associated ProcessInstance or FlowNodeInstance is instantiated.
Since:
6.0.0
Author:
Feng Hui, Celine Souchet
